nhc_headline: ...HENRIETTE INTENSIFYING QUICKLY WELL NORTHEAST OF THE HAWAIIAN ISLANDS...
summary: ...HENRIETTE INTENSIFYING QUICKLY WELL NORTHEAST OF THE HAWAIIAN ISLANDS... As of 5:00 AM HST Sun Aug 10 the center of Henriette was located near 24.7, -151.5 with movement NW at 16 mph. The minimum central pressure was 1000 mb with maximum sustained winds of about 60 mph.
